No errors is defined.
.LP
\fIDa followin sections is informative.\fP
.SH EXAMPLES
.SS Gettin Date n' Time Formattin Information
.LP
Da followin example returns a pointa ta a strang containin date
and time formattin shiznit, as defined up in the
\fILC_TIME\fP category of tha current locale.
.sp
.RS
.nf

\fB#include <time.h>
#include <langinfo.h>
\&...
strftime(datestring, sizeof(datestring), nl_langinfo(D_T_FMT), tm);
\&...
\fP
.fi
.RE
.SH APPLICATION USAGE
.LP
Da array pointed ta by tha return value should not be modified by
the program yo, but may be modified by further calls to
